        "notes": "<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Python String</h3>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>Strings are sequence of characters written inside quotes. It can include letters, numbers, symbols and</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>spaces. Python does not have a separate character type.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• A single character is treated as a string of length one.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• Strings are commonly used for text handling and manipulation.</p>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Creating a String</h3>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>Strings can be created using either Single quotes ' '</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• Double quotes \" \"</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• Triple quotes ''' ''' or \"\"\" \"\"\" (used for multiline string</p>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Example:</h3>\n<pre style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace;'><code>name = \"Python\"\ncity = 'Jodhpur'\nmessage = \"\"\"Welcome to Python Programming\"\"\"</code></pre>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Characteristics of Python Strings</h3>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Immutable:</strong> Once a string is created, we cannot change it. Any operation in terms of modifying a</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>string will actually make a new string.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Ordered:</strong> Strings are ordered collections of characters where each character has a fixed index</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>(starting from 0). We can access the characters using their position.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Iterable:</strong> We can iterate through each character of a string using Python loops, like for and while.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Support Slicing:</strong> We can slice a string to extract substrings with the help of [start : end] syntax.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Unicode Support:</strong> By default, strings in Python 3 are stored as Unicode. This allows us to handle</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>international languages and emojis efficiently.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Dynamic Length:</strong> We can initialize a string of any length, from an empty string to a string consisting of</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>millions of characters.</p>\n<p style='margin: 8px 0 8px 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6;'>• <strong style='color: #00bfff;'>Can contain any characters:</strong> A string can include letters (A-Z, a-z), digits (0-9), special characters</p>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>like @, #, $, %, etc., spaces, tabs, and even newlines.</p>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Accessing Characters in String</h3>\n<pre class='diagram' style='font-family: monospace; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 8px 0; overflow-x: auto; color: #5bdcae;'>0          1          2          3          4          5          6</pre>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>C</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>O</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>D</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>E</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>A</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Z</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Y</th></tr></table></div>\n<pre class='diagram' style='font-family: monospace; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.25); padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 8px 0; overflow-x: auto; color: #5bdcae;'>-7         -6         -5         -4         -3         -2         -1</pre>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Example:</h3>\n<pre style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace;'><code>1. # python program to access characters in a string\n2. # given string\n3. s = \"CODEAZY\"\n4. print(\"Given String:\", s)\n5. # accessing characters using indexing\n6. print(\"s[0] =\", s[0])\n7. print(\"s[5] =\", s[5])</code></pre>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Accessing String with Negative Indexing</h3>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Example:</h3>\n<pre style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace;'><code>1. # python program to access characters from back of the string\n2. # given string\n3. s = \"CODEAZY\"\n4. print(\"Given String:\", s)\n5. # accessing characters using negative indexing\n6. print(\"s[-1] =\", s[-1])\n7. print(\"s[-6] =\", s[-6])</code></pre>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Slicing</h3>\n<p style='margin: 12px 0; color: #bbb; line-height: 1.65;'>The format for slicing a string is string_name[start : end]</p>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Example:</h3>\n<pre style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace;'><code>1. # python program to slice a string\n2. # given string\n3. s = “codeazy\"\n4. print(\"Given String:\", s)\n5. # getting characters from index 1 to 4\n6. print(\"s[1:5] =\", s[1:5])\n7. print(\"s[:4] =\", s[:4])\n8. print(\"s[4:] =\", s[4:])\n9. print(\"s[::-1] =\", s[::-1])</code></pre>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Function</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>S.No</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>String Functions</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Description</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Program</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Output</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>1</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>len()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Returns total characters.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(len(text))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>6</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>2</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>max()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Returns largest character.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>print(max(\"Python\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>y</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>3</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>min()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Returns smallest<br>character.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>print(min(\"Python\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>P</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>4</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>sorted()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Sorts characters.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>print(sorted(\"python\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>['P', 'h', 'n', 'o',<br>'t', 'y']</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>S.No</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>String Method</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Description</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Program</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Output</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>1</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>upper()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Converts string into<br>uppercase.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"python\"<br>print(text.upper())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>PYTHON</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>2</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>lower()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Converts string into<br>lowercase.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"PYTHON\"<br>print(text.lower())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>python</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>3</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>capitalize()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Capitalizes first letter</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"python programming\"<br>print(text.capitalize())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python<br>programming</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>4</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>title()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Capitalizes first letter of every<br>word.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"python programming\"<br>print(text.title())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python<br>Programming</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>5</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>swapcase()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Changes uppercase to<br>lowercase and vice versa.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"PyThOn\"<br>print(text.swapcase())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>pYtHoN</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>6</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>casefold()</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Used for aggressive lowercase<br>comparison.</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"HELLO\"<br>print(text.casefold())</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>hello</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>7</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>strip()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Removes spaces from both sides.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.strip())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>8</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>lstrip()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Removes left spaces.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.lstrip())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>9</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>rstrip()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Removes right spaces.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.rstrip())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>10</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>replace()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Replaces old value with new<br>value.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"I like Java\"<br>print(text.replace(\"Java\",<br>\"Python\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>I like Python</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>11</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>split()</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Converts string into list.</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python Java C\"<br>print(text.split())</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>['Python', 'Java',<br>'C']</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>12</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>join()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Join list elements into string.<br>join() is considered one of the most useful<br>Python string methods for combining<br>iterable strings.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>data = ['Python', 'Java',<br>'C']<br>print(\" - \".join(data))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Python - Java - C</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>13</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>find()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Finds substring position.<br>Or we can say that it finds the first<br>occurrence of the specified value.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.find(\"t\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>2<br>If not found:<br>-1</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>14</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>index()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Same as find() but gives error if not found.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.index(\"h\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>3</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>15</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>count()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Counts occurrences.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python<br>Programming\"<br>print(text.count(\"m\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>16</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>startswith()</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks starting word.</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.startswith(\"Py\"))</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>17</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>endswith()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks ending word.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.endswith(\"on\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>18</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>isalpha()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks alphabet only.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.isalpha())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>19</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>isdigit()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks digits only.<br>Use isdigit() when you only want standard<br>•<br>decimal digits, possibly in various scripts.<br>Great for parsing IDs or zip codes.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"12345\"<br>print(text.isdigit())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>20</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>isnumeric()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks numeric values.<br>Use isnumeric() when you want to accept<br>•<br>numeric forms like fractions or superscripts.<br>Useful in math processing or display parsing.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"123\"<br>print(text.isnumeric())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>21</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>isalnum()</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks alphabets + numbers.</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python123\"<br>print(text.isalnum())</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>22</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>islower()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks lowercase.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"python\"<br>print(text.islower())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>23</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>isupper()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks uppercase.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"PYTHON\"<br>print(text.isupper())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>24</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>istitle()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Checks title case.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python Programming\"<br>print(text.istitle())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>True</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>25</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>center()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Aligns string at center.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.center(10, '*'))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>**Python**</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Method</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>26</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>zfill()</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Adds zeros at beginning.</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>num = \"25\"<br>print(num.zfill(5))</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>00025</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>27</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>partition()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Splits string into 3 parts.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python-Java\"<br>print(text.partition(\"-\"))</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>('Python', '-<br>', 'Java')</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>28</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>encode()</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Converts string into encoded bytes.</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>text = \"Python\"<br>print(text.encode())</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>b'Python'</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>String Operators</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>S.No</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>String Operators</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Program</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Output</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>1</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>CONCATENATION (+)</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>A = \"HELLO”<br>B = \"WORLD”<br>PRINT(A + \" \" + B)</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>HELLO WORLD</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>2</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>REPETITION (*)</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>PRINT(\"PYTHON \" * 3)</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>PYTHON PYTHON<br>PYTHON</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>3</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>MEMBERSHIP OPERATOR</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>TEXT = \"PYTHON”<br>PRINT(\"P\" IN TEXT)<br>PRINT(\"JAVA\" NOT IN TEXT)</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>TRUE<br>TRUE</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Escape Character</h3>\n<div class='table-responsive'><table class='notes-table' style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 24px 0; color: #ccc; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.01); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Escape Character</th><th style='padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.08); color: #00bfff; font-weight: 600; text-align: left; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Meaning</th></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>\\n</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>New Line</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>\\t</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Tab Space</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>\\\\</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Backslash</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>\\'</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Single Quote</td></tr><tr style='border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>\\\"</td><td style='padding: 12px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);'>Double Quote</td></tr></table></div>\n<h3 style='color: #fff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;'>Example:</h3>\n<pre style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0; overflow-x: auto; font-family: monospace;'><code>print(\"Hello\\nWorld\")</code></pre>"
      }
    ]
